# 📱 Mobile Sales Dashboard – Power BI Project

## 📌 Project Overview
The **Mobile Sales Dashboard** is an end-to-end Business Intelligence project built using **Power BI** to analyze mobile phone sales performance across brands, cities, payment methods, and time periods.
The dashboard converts raw transactional data into meaningful insights through interactive visualizations, KPI tracking, and dynamic filtering to support data-driven decision-making.

## 🎯 Project Objectives
* Analyze overall mobile sales performance
* Track sales trends across months and weekdays
* Compare sales performance among mobile brands
* Understand customer purchasing behavior
* Evaluate customer rating distribution
* Identify high-performing locations and models

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies
| Tool             | Purpose                        |
| ---------------- | ------------------------------ |
| Power BI Desktop | Dashboard Development          |
| Power Query      | Data Cleaning & Transformation |
| DAX              | KPI Calculations               |
| Excel            | Data Source                    |
| Data Modeling    | Relationship Building          |

## 📂 Dataset Information
The dataset contains:
  * Transaction ID
  * Mobile Brand
  * Mobile Model
  * Sales Amount
  * Quantity Sold
  * Customer Rating
  * Payment Method
  * Transaction Date
  * City / Location

## ⚙️ Data Preparation Process

### Data Cleaning
✔ Removed missing values
✔ Corrected data types
✔ Removed duplicates

### Data Transformation
✔ Created calculated columns
✔ Built data relationships
✔ Created DAX measures

## 🧮 DAX Measures

```DAX
Total Sales =
SUM(Sales[Total_Sales])

Total Quantity =
SUM(Sales[Quantity])

Total Transactions =
COUNT(Sales[Transaction_ID])

Average Price =
DIVIDE([Total Sales],[Total Quantity])
```

## 📊 Dashboard Features

### KPI Cards
* 💰 Total Sales
* 📦 Total Quantity
* 🧾 Total Transactions
* 📈 Average Price

### Interactive Filters
* Brand
* Mobile Model
* Payment Method
* Month Selection
* Reset Filters

### Visualizations
* Pie Chart → Payment Method Analysis
* Map → Quantity by City
* Bar Chart → Sales by Mobile Model
* Funnel Chart → Customer Ratings
* Line Chart → Sales by Day
* Trend Chart → Quantity by Month
* Table → Brand Performance

## 📈 Key Insights
* Generated insights from **₹769M+ Total Sales**
* Identified top-performing mobile models
* Evaluated customer satisfaction trends
* Compared payment method usage
* Monitored weekday and monthly sales performance
* Analyzed city-wise product demand

## 🔍 Business Questions Answered
* Which brand generated the highest sales?
* Which payment method is most preferred?
* Which city sold the highest quantity?
* Which month performed best?
* How do customer ratings impact sales?

